{"tid":1082674,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"恕我直言 香港人必須自認高質","createTime":"2019-03-29T06:10:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T18:04:04.000Z","uid":104767,"like":222,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"58b7796ff4245d86e2663f21175761316656ed75","tid":1082674,"uid":104767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T06:10:20.000Z","msg":"民族自豪感係凝眾社會力量既不二法門，就算香港人低質，必要時隱惡揚善無可避免。要受國際社會尊重，自己必先睇得起自己。<br />\n<br />\n存亡之際，踩港撚幾客觀都好，都唔該收一收把口。香港人有咩唔好，應該俾啲建設性意見。出個post 話香港人低質，然後就argument ended, 有撚實際作用？唯一作用就係令香港人自卑，愧於自己身份，最後放棄香港。<br />\n<br />\n學老共講法，踩港而冇俾建設性意見既人，係香港人既敵人，必須根除。中共從來都分敵我，香港人都要有敵我意識，從心底認為自己比中國人優勝，先係踏出救港第一步。"},{"pid":"ec50a8e4e94d7003a008f5cb7faed30467a01bf4","tid":1082674,"uid":157362,"like":8,"dislike":215,"score":-207,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T06:10:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"82c6e45d71f92b17f8d05c83a1da7f24c3bfa391","tid":1082674,"uid":33651,"like":2,"dislike":58,"score":-56,"quote":{"pid":"ec50a8e4e94d7003a008f5cb7faed30467a01bf4","tid":1082674,"uid":157362,"like":8,"dislike":215,"score":-207,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T06:10:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T06:11:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4JEaTE3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4JEaTE3.jpg&h=76343506&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f7adfa45370c5581051bd2aafc81ea1780c7d18d","tid":1082674,"uid":162866,"like":0,"dislike":53,"score":-53,"quote":{"pid":"82c6e45d71f92b17f8d05c83a1da7f24c3bfa391","tid":1082674,"uid":33651,"like":2,"dislike":58,"score":-56,"quote":{"pid":"ec50a8e4e94d7003a008f5cb7faed30467a01bf4","tid":1082674,"uid":157362,"like":8,"dislike":215,"score":-207,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T06:10:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T06:11:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4JEaTE3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4JEaTE3.jpg&h=76343506&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20